RULE Proj:PrescriptiveDayltgException
  DESCRIPTION
    "Whether EXCEPTION 1 or 2 to Section 130.1(d)2 (Prescriptive Daylighting
     Requirements) apply to the project. "  
  HELP
    ""  
  REFERENCE 
    
  INPUTCLASS
    Default    
  DEFAULT 
